# TagIfd0.GpsInfo field

A pointer to the GPS Info IFD. The Interoperability structure of the GPS Info IFD, like that of Exif IFD, has no image data.

```csharp
public static readonly Tag GpsInfo;
```

## Remarks

Expected type is UInt32.
